1
00:00:00,590 --> 00:00:04,910
[Fated Hearts – My Deep Feelings You Don't Understand]

2
00:00:04,970 --> 00:00:06,050
[On-set of “Fated Hearts”] [Filming in progress]

3
00:00:06,050 --> 00:00:07,970
[Hair sticking to face]

4
00:00:09,210 --> 00:00:11,310
The wind won't stop blowing.

5
00:00:12,200 --> 00:00:14,690
[Hair covering face]

6
00:00:15,400 --> 00:00:16,530
Hair.

7
00:00:17,460 --> 00:00:18,290
[You too]

8
00:00:18,130 --> 00:00:19,300
Your earlobe.

9
00:00:18,860 --> 00:00:19,940
[Let me help you]

10
00:00:21,620 --> 00:00:23,590
[Mutual aid]

11
00:00:27,060 --> 00:00:27,500
Hair.

12
00:00:27,500 --> 00:00:28,600
Again.

13
00:00:29,380 --> 00:00:30,650
One more time.

14
00:00:30,200 --> 00:00:30,990
[Hairstylist emergency online]

15
00:00:30,730 --> 00:00:32,360
The wind's getting worse.

16
00:00:32,360 --> 00:00:33,130
What now?

17
00:00:37,160 --> 00:00:38,130
Come on.

18
00:00:38,130 --> 00:00:39,230
You can do it.

19
00:00:38,150 --> 00:00:39,780
[Self-encouragement]

20
00:00:40,010 --> 00:00:41,160
[Action!]

21
00:00:43,030 --> 00:00:44,330
Don't cry.

22
00:00:45,350 --> 00:00:46,180
[Awkward]

23
00:00:46,200 --> 00:00:47,430
I'm not crying.

24
00:00:46,250 --> 00:00:47,550
[Stubborn]

25
00:00:48,800 --> 00:00:50,460
It's just too windy earlier.

26
00:00:51,760 --> 00:00:54,160
Where's the wind even coming from indoors?

27
00:00:54,600 --> 00:00:55,560
Doesn't matter—

28
00:00:55,560 --> 00:00:57,090
the wind's just too strong.

29
00:01:00,590 --> 00:01:02,090
Don't worry.

30
00:01:00,850 --> 00:01:06,770
[Deep affection]

31
00:01:02,090 --> 00:01:03,710
I'm here.

32
00:01:03,730 --> 00:01:06,190
I won't let the wind or sand blow on you again.

33
00:01:06,930 --> 00:01:08,440
[Exchange a smile]

34
00:01:08,780 --> 00:01:10,100
[Blows gently]

35
00:01:11,080 --> 00:01:11,940
[Teasing]

36
00:01:12,460 --> 00:01:14,700
I helped you blow away that awful strand of hair.

37
00:01:13,410 --> 00:01:14,750
[And you're not even thanking me?]

38
00:01:14,700 --> 00:01:16,000
You blew it away with your hand!

39
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:16,730
Like this.

40
00:01:16,730 --> 00:01:18,060
I'm being so affectionate here.

41
00:01:18,060 --> 00:01:19,060
He's right there.

42
00:01:21,130 --> 00:01:21,760
I said—

43
00:01:21,760 --> 00:01:24,490
I'll never let the wind and sand blow on you again.

44
00:01:26,150 --> 00:01:27,030
[No giggling]

45
00:01:27,920 --> 00:01:29,700
[Giggling]
